# 12. The World

The game world contains five major regions.

The Four Kingdoms

* Chola
* Chera
* Pandya
* Pallava

The Central Region

Velir Aram

Hidden beneath Velir Aram lies the forgotten civilization known as **Ezhamandalam (The Seventh Realm)**.

This location serves as the central point of conflict, exploration, and long-term strategic advantage.

